org.eclipse.collections.impl.stack.mutable.primitive

Class CharArrayStack

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.collections.impl.stack.mutable.primitive.CharArrayStack
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Externalizable, Serializable, CharIterable, PrimitiveIterable, CharStack, MutableCharStack

    @NotThreadSafe
public final class CharArrayStack
extends Object
implements MutableCharStack, Externalizable
    CharArrayStack is similar to ArrayStack, and is memory-optimized for char primitives. This file was automatically generated from template file primitiveArrayStack.stg.
